          "description": "## Dossier **payment/Init payment**\n\nInitie une demande de paiement.\n\n### POST **/api/v2/payment** _(Bearer)_\n\n**Requête**\n\n```\nPOST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/payment\nAuthorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}\nContent-Type: application/json\n{\n  \"payer\":      \"2376xxxxxxxx\",\n  \"amount\":     \"100\",\n  \"externalId\": \"votreIdUniqe\",\n  \"description\":\"Test de paiement\",\n  \"callback\":   \"https://votresite.com/webhook/freemopay\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n**Réponse (200 OK)**\n\n```\n{\n  \"reference\": \"uuid-de-transaction\",\n  \"status\":    \"SUCCESS\",  // INITIALIZATION_SUCCESS ou FAILED\n  \"message\":   \"\"\n}\n\n ```\n\n### POST **/api/v2/payment** _(Basic Auth)_\n\nMême schéma, avec Basic Auth en lieu et place du Bearer.\n\nGET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/payment/:reference  \nAuthorization: Bearer bearerToken"
